1. Write Ruby program to get the ruby version with patch number.
~$ ruby -v
Ruby Version: ruby 2.3.1p112
Ruby Patch Level: 112

2. Write a Ruby program to display the current date and time.
~$ date
Current Date and Time: понеділок, 21 червня 2021 23:46:15 +0300

3. Write a Ruby program to create a new string which is n copies of a given string where n is a non-negative integer.
Sample Output:
a
aa
aaa
aaaa
aaaaa

if n > 0 do
  until i <= n
    print "a"
    i+=1
  end
end
